#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/CLAHE_dialog.ui:93
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Please, make sure to remove all black borders or other\n"
"    stacking residuals by cropping the image. If you don't,\n"
"    artifacts may appear."
