#: src/gui-gtk4/uifiles/bdeconv_dialog.ui:1481
msgid ""
"Sets an early stop criterion for the Richardson-Lucy algorithm to prevent "
"noise amplification. Deconvolution will stop early if the average pixel "
"difference ratio between subsequent iterations is less than this value."
msgstr ""
"Legt ein frühes Stoppkriterium für den Richardson-Lucy-Algorithmus fest, um "
